# Private content (videos, CV, profile photo, links) — kept off public GitHub.
# Populated locally and on the deployment VM; bind-mounted into the container.
# README is kept tracked so people landing on the public repo see what's here.
/artifacts/*
!/artifacts/README.md

# Data Doctor runtime artifacts (FAISS indices + trained models, ~330 MB).
# Kept in the working tree so deploy.sh can push them to the HF Space, but too
# big for GitHub. The HF Space repo (git-LFS) is their versioned home.
/projects/health_assistant/artifacts/
